Thanks so much for all your feedback we re proud to say that Halo is now available for iPads! We ve created a unique iPad experience so you can make the most of your journaling on a larger device. Now you can type your long reflection entries with your keyboard or write a quick goal setting Moment with your Apple Pencil. We strive to make journaling as inclusive as possible and in this update you ll find that we ve included VoiceOver support for those who need it.
